data.description: Just under 25 acres in good location just 10 miles from Bowie. Good, fenced property with trees and a stock tank in the back. Great open concept floor plan in this 3bedroom 2 bath home with bonus room for small office or overnight guest. House features oversized master with large bath walk in closet.
